25 years ago, our #SingleMarket was created.
European citizens now fully embrace the freedoms and opportunities that were only a dream for their parents and grandparents → https://t.co/YNCPJG9vk5 #EUandMe https://t.co/yoAKfLrsAs

How digital is your country?
🇩🇰, 🇸🇪, 🇫🇮 and 🇳🇱 top the ranking! 
We need a genuine #DigitalSingleMarket to boost EU digital performance. https://t.co/aex16Adxxb

Taking action at a local level is the way to make yours a green city.
Take part in one of many #EUGreenWeek partner events close to you and get inspired → https://t.co/oCV9vg3LUS https://t.co/7L9WOm9SOF

Whatever happens, the #FutureofEurope must be built with citizens. 
We are launching an online public consultation addressed to all Europeans → https://t.co/5TAsxw3F8D https://t.co/4cyq85YrWJ

Only few days to go...

📌 Check out the #TeamJunckerEU calendar for the week including #EUGreenWeek and #EUdialogues → https://t.co/1tf3aHhCgI https://t.co/PjOJ11U3oq

data.text:
This week we took action to protect Europeans from air pollution.
Standing up for the need to breathe clean air, we are referring 🇫🇷 🇩🇪 🇭🇺 🇮🇹 🇷🇴 🇬🇧 to the Court of Justice of the EU and issuing additional letters of formal notice to 🇩🇪 🇮🇹 🇱🇺 🇬🇧
#AirQuality https://t.co/ObM2DRxL15

Your gender should not determine your success!
Discover the #SheIsWe voices and join the movement.
Who is she for you? https://t.co/IapT5k5evL #EDD18 https://t.co/blDQiefldi

We are taking stock of our #BetterRegulation approach to make our policies:
💡 more transparent
💡 more efficient
💡 closer to your needs
Check out the roadmap and leave your comments → https://t.co/js7F7RlvEJ #EUHaveYourSay https://t.co/SGGkO7bOku

Mobility is crossing a new technological frontier. 
With our new #MobilityEU package, we want to help our industry stay ahead of the curve and get closer to a triple zero: emissions, congestion and accidents. https://t.co/m3HCTGGJwZ

In Latvia, a young beekeeper wanted to grow his family's honey bee farm. The EU gave him a push to buy his equipment and increase his exports → https://t.co/GjsASd51FW  #investEU #WorldBeeDay https://t.co/GXDSORLXvv

Bottles, bags or cups: single-use plastics represent half of the items found on EU beaches but can take 500 years to breakdown into smaller pieces. 
We will soon present our proposal on single-use plastics. #PlasticsStrategy https://t.co/UwcAEBQqJh

Our new EU #DataProtection rules will enter into application on Friday! 
With a sharp eye, Belgian cartoonist Pierre Kroll illustrated the many challenges of protecting personal data online. 
Know your rights → https://t.co/E8MqO8FFl7  #GDPR https://t.co/ZVCwFT4f8C

Today we celebrate the first ever #WorldBeeDay! 🐝
Finally a spotlight on the tireless work of bees and other pollinators that is so essential to our wellbeing and food security.
More on our work to stop their decline: https://t.co/yPWcDJ8gxz https://t.co/0o1ZWDRyxi

We have a responsibility to act to prevent lost generations. 
The EU is now a global leader in bringing children back to school. 8% of our humanitarian aid budget goes to education in emergencies this year – 8 times up from 2015.
We aim to reach 10% in 2019 https://t.co/jCeMxSIAu8

#EUHaveYourSay in our public consultation on our Strategic Environmental Assessment.
How important is it to you that stakeholders and the public are informed about the potential environmental impacts of public plans and programmes? → https://t.co/AYEYD2dIdr https://t.co/EDnBRJ3lWr

This week the EU-Western Balkans Summit in Sofia confirmed the European perspective of the region.
It also set out actions to strengthen cooperation in the areas of connectivity, security and the rule of law. #FutureofEurope #WesternBalkans https://t.co/ruwUzlsCbW

Every year, 18 million applications for short-stay Schengen visas are processed. We propose to upgrade #EUVisa Information System to 
✔️allow for more background checks
✔️close security information gaps
✔️ensure full interoperability
Learn more → https://t.co/IOtHuo6CTZ https://t.co/SUDyxokRaA

We are completing our #MobilityEU agenda with our third and final set of actions to allow all Europeans to benefit from safer traffic, less polluting vehicles and more advanced technological solutions → https://t.co/x0IyaU1WBZ https://t.co/YrSXvBMHBc

We are on the #EURoad2Sibiu!
In one year, the 27 EU Leaders will meet at an extraordinary summit in Sibiu, Romania to decide on the way forward for the #FutureofEurope.  Our end destination will be a more united, democratic and stronger Union → https://t.co/noyyw7TwSS https://t.co/K3YZrj7vTs

It is time to decide what the #FutureofEurope at 27 should be. 
96 Europeans from all around Europe prepared 12 simple questions to be asked to all EU citizens. 
Now it's your turn to answer and share your ideas → https://t.co/5TAsxw3F8D https://t.co/PJsX8OxLr4

Congratulations to the 6 winners of the #Natura2000 Award 🎉🇪🇺
Thank you for your dedication and love for nature!
Learn more about these inspiring EU projects → https://t.co/4K49twxyMJ https://t.co/491sPrUKok

How can we improve education in emergencies?
• better access to learning opportunities for youth
• quality education and training
• ensure education is protected from attacks
• rapid and innovative education responses
#EUEducationEmpowers https://t.co/IwghIz1742

We have a responsibility to act to prevent lost generations.
The EU is a global leader in bringing children back to school. 8% of our humanitarian aid budget goes to education in emergencies this year.
We aim to reach 10% in 2019.
https://t.co/y9yYvroRPV #EUintheWorld https://t.co/NO0KeHwbQR

Urgent EU humanitarian aid has been dispatched to contain the #Ebola outbreak in the Democratic Republic of Congo.
Our funding and humanitarian flight service will help get medical teams, equipment and supplies to the affected health zone.
https://t.co/Fbs7pCgfVt https://t.co/cNUMYjIBOv

How digital is your country?
We are publishing the results of the 2018 Digital Economy and Society Index, monitoring the performance of EU countries in digital connectivity, digital skills and digitisation of businesses → https://t.co/vvkZiWXBku #DigitalSingleMarket https://t.co/fKYDD6iDJ7
We are acting to protect the interests of EU companies investing in Iran and remain fully committed to the continued, full and effective implementation of the #IranDeal → https://t.co/RKsPy2a1Kg
Europe united on Iran and trade relations with the US, improving connectivity and security in the #WesternBalkans region. #EUCO https://t.co/wHUr4UtP89

⏰ 7 days to go... 
Don't be blind to your new rights on #DataProtection → https://t.co/eUYVho41OG https://t.co/NVkpBtKdmU

EU emergency assistance of €3 million in aid will help provide basic supplies to civilians in need in Gaza.
It is essential that critical goods and equipment are allowed to enter in a timely manner. https://t.co/FkMfA0PfAx https://t.co/NC06wHLQhe

Mobility is crossing a new technological frontier.
With our new #MobilityEU package, we want to help our industry stay ahead of the curve and get closer to a triple zero: emissions, congestion and accidents. https://t.co/PoGiHvB5BI

Today's summit between EU leaders and #WesternBalkans partners in Sofia confirmed the European perspective of the region and actions to strengthen cooperation in connectivity, security and the rule of law.
https://t.co/EMT8cTopxU #FutureofEurope https://t.co/ZuTU5yHakZ

✔️allow for more background checks
